New Major Version! Quick Navigation: Easily navigate to your favorite places with handy thumb controls. Continue Watching: Pick up watching your favorite episodes right where you left off. Live Schedule: Quickly find current upcoming and past shows being broadcast on BYUtv. Watch live TV or watch most shows on demand directly from the app! my BYUtv: The place to find all of your followed shows playlists downloaded episodes for offline viewing and recently watched episodes.

Welcome to the completely redesigned BYUtv app. In addition to watching your favorite BYUtv shows live and on demand we re now brining new content organized around your favorite shows like social media blog posts cast bios photo galleries show merchandise and more. And for the first time ever you can download episodes to your iOS device for offline viewing when you login to your free BYUtv account. We hope you enjoy the all new BYUtv app.
